title: VA - Best Of House 19 [Progressive/Deep/Tech House]
description:
Focus is on Progressive House, sometimes touching the Tribal side of things. Though there's also regular Deep House and a few Tech-House tracks (mostly remixes by Forteba) to complement the release. Most tracks in 320kbps or V2, older ones in 192kbps.

This release is dedicated to my mom, who passed away from cancer in January 2013.

I have a thread going over at Discogs where I'm trying to ID some tracks. Please have a listen at: http://www.discogs.com/groups/topic/373674

Full track list:
Total tracks: 127
Total playtime: 17hrs 06min

Enjoy!
